们将加强相关的培训。”而在东方甄选致歉之前，主播天权在其个人账号发表道歉信称，他在直播时说了江小白不是白酒，给大家造成了误会，也给江小白品牌方造成了困扰，这确实是他的责任，“表示非常的抱歉”。 然而，9日深夜，江小白再发声明“正面刚”天权的道歉。江小白称，天权道歉信以其个人微博发布，并未署名盖章，“不接受这种非正式形式和态度不诚恳的道歉”，公司将进一步通过投诉和法律维护自身权益。 东方甄选主播天权在直播中究竟说了些什么？江小白方面为何深夜再发声明表示不接受天权的道歉？《每日经济新闻·将进酒》记者就此进行了采访。称江小白“不是白酒”，东方甄选主播道歉 江小白深夜声明：不接受"},"attached_info":"CkAI/9vyjLeTyKgeEAMaCTEwOTgxMzA2MCC8/tq1BjAAOIYBQAZyCTY2MzkwOTE2N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"200 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-abd3978a34ebbb716305203984572b52_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1723306736.67292","card_id":"Q_663925890","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":663925890,"title":"2024 巴黎奥运会艺术体操团体全能决赛，中国队艺术体操队夺冠，如何评价本场比赛她们的表现？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/663925890","type":"question","created":1723274986,"answer_count":42,"follower_count":80,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[25712,234364,1344967],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I/9vyjLeTyKgeEAMaCTEwOTgxNjc0NiDqrdy1BjAAOFBAB3IJNjYzOTI1ODkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"169 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8d72accaf07ce196225c2e5ef25145a_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1723306736.68596","card_id":"Q_663873095","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":663873095,"title":"马龙说巴黎是奥运生涯最后一站，退役还需考虑，等他退役中国男乒还会出现「三驾马车」这样有统治力的组合吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/6638730